  "text": "WiMAX already specifies [CITATION_1] that a SS should provide channel measurements that can form a basis for channel quality estimates. These are either Received Signal Strength Indicators or may be Carrier-to-Noise-and Interference Ratio measurements made over modulated carrier preambles.",
